\cb31 Her curiosity flows beyond the sterile room, past the crumbling towers, dodging the pink giant flowers in the sky.\cb1 \
\cb31 Flowing further and further...\cb1 \
\cb31 "Looks just like a cracked, stinky egg~"\cb1 \
\cb31 "But I want to experience it for a while..."\cb1 \
