\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 This is a grand, bustling plaza.\cb1 \
\cb31 On a stage towering above everyone else, someone is muttering something.\cb1 \
\cb31 A voice calls out her name, and many people crowd around. The dazed flower is transplanted onto the stage, gunpowder still fresh in her hair.\cb1 \
\cb31 The black box flickers with light brighter than stars, and small metal patches are pinned onto both the older and the younger one, both equally at a loss for what to do.\cb1 \
\cb31 This recognition also means that from this moment on, she is "Seed," and the robot that has always been by her side is now "Seed Sr."\cb1 \
\cb31 "Did I do well?"\cb1 \
\cb31 "Of course, you're our pride... this codename is proof of that, Seed."\cb1 \
